946,IssuesEvent,2015-05-12 17:42:32+00:00,22937749,rasbt/mlxtend,5618407,rasbt,,,closed,Linear Regression Plotting not working,[],[],1,"Hi, First of all ... awesome work man !! 
I am new to python and after moving from R on kaggle found link to 'mlxtend'.

Now my issue is following code not plotting anything. 

