2061,IssuesEvent,2018-05-01 21:44:03+00:00,3489194,davidhalter/jedi,748594,davidhalter,,,closed,completion error for groupby when DataFrame is created in a function,[],[],8,"The first script runs OK:
```python
import jedi
good_source = \
""""""from pandas import read_stata
bar_var = read_stata('bad_file')
bad_var.groupby(['aa'])['bb'].mean()
""""""
