2833,IssuesEvent,2017-04-21 09:45:04+00:00,32283257,philpep/testinfra,387511,philpep,,,closed,RFC enhanced readability of testinfra fixtures,"[{'id': 187660502, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/philpep/testinfra/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}]",[],8,"This is a proposal of a future syntax to replace current fixture system:

```python
# capitalized fixture name that must be repeated for each test declaration
def test_something(Command, Service, Sudo, File, Package):
    [...]
```

Proposition 1: Just one fixture to access all modules and remove capitalization of first letter (could be named Server or Testinfra or Connection or Backend)

```python
def test_something(Server):
    assert Server.service(""nginx"").is_running
    assert Server.package(""nginx"").version = ""1.4.3""
```

Proposition 2: Import

```python
import pytest
from testinfra.modules import Service

# on whole module or for each testinfra test
pytestmark = pytest.mark.testinfra

def test_something():
    assert Service(""nginx"").is_running
```

Migration path: DeprecationWarning for v1, drop old usage in v2",{},{}
