4447,IssuesEvent,2016-12-12 11:19:07+00:00,71888065,cr0hn/aiohttp-swagger,3034091,denismakogon,,,opened,Support response object and error references in API spec,[],[],0,"Currently only handlers are being analyzed for docstrings. So as part of the docstring it is possible to mention response object and errors using next notation:

