ultimately yields 
`Failed to connect to share Data\Users\Shared\Everyone\: SMB SessionError: STATUS_INVALID_PARAMETER(An invalid parameter was passed to a service or function.)`

`crackmapexec rg-file01 -d rg -u ""user"" -p ""pass"" --verbose --share ""Data"" --spider --pattern pass`
