6049,IssuesEvent,2016-12-15 10:30:35+00:00,27728976,eisensheng/pytest-catchlog,159967,mgedmin,,,opened,log_print in pytest.ini has no effect,[],[],0,"## Steps to reproduce

Create a `pytest.ini`:

```ini
