7112,IssuesEvent,2018-05-18 12:47:30+00:00,34864402,apache/incubator-mxnet,30927640,GoodJoey,47359,apache,closed,question: how to speed up the process of feeding data.,"[{'id': 355414483, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/apache/incubator-mxnet/labels/Data-loading', 'name': 'Data-loading', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': False}, {'id': 823355562, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/apache/incubator-mxnet/labels/Feature%20request', 'name': 'Feature request', 'color': '0e8a16', 'default': False}]",[],2,"hi, i tried to do the training on the 8 gpus server, but it turns out that it's not faster than when using 4 gpus.
