7952,IssuesEvent,2018-03-06 16:25:40+00:00,648332,assimp/assimp,2323156,kimkulling,265533,assimp,closed,DAE Node Names,"[{'id': 244436167, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/assimp/assimp/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'bfe5bf', 'default': True}]",[],2,"DAE file nodes have generally three attributes:
**id**, **name** and **sid**.

Assimp returns the **id** attribute value for any node name.

In some engines, like Unity, the **name** field is used instead.

A config can be created to choose between **id** and **name** field
when returning this information.

Maybe I will take this task, just letting it here to remember.
",{},{}
