<!--- describe how this could be used / the use case for this icon -->

XRP is the cryptocurrency symbol of the world's third-largest cryptocurrency by market cap. Font-Awesome already supports #1 and #2 respectively (btc and ethereum). Please consider adding XRP!

Not to be confused with the logo of Ripple (which is a company), XRP is a digital asset (not a company) so is a totally separate entity. 

Here (on the Ripple corporate website https://ripple.com/xrp/) you can see both the Ripple logo and the XRP symbol.

The XRP symbol is the official outcome of a community endeavour to come up with a unicode-friendly symbol.

Thanks,
Pete

