10980,IssuesEvent,2016-08-18 18:20:44+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/gcloud-python,520669,dhermes,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,opened,Use GAX generated libraries for Datastore and Bigtable,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/gcloud-python/labels/bigtable', 'name': 'bigtable', 'color': '0052cc'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/gcloud-python/labels/datastore', 'name': 'datastore', 'color': '0052cc'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/GoogleCloudPlatform/gcloud-python/labels/gRPC', 'name': 'gRPC', 'color': 'd4c5f9'}]",[],0,"@bjwatson WDYT of this? We are currently generating via `protoc` with our own `Makefile`s ([datastore][1] and [bigtable][2]).

