https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-python/blob/master/bigtable/google/cloud/bigtable/row_filters.py#L171

the documentation asserts that the valid range for a RowSampleFilter is `[0.0, 1.0]`.  In fact, it is the open interval `(0.0, 1.0)`.  The server rejects both `0.0` and `1.0`.

