##### ISSUE TYPE
Enhancement of functionality available for other AFs.

##### OS
Ubuntu 16.04 LTS and others

##### VERSION
```
ExaBGP : 3.4.18
Python : 2.7.11+ (default, Apr 17 2016, 14:00:29)  [GCC 5.3.1 20160413]
Uname  : #50-Ubuntu SMP Wed Jul 13 00:07:12 UTC 2016
```

##### ENVIRONMENT 
```
[exabgp.daemon]
user = 'exabgp'
```


##### CONFIGURATION
```
group EXA_AFX2_2_IAVRR {
        local-as 65060;
        peer-as 65060;
        router-id 10.0.99.9;
        local-address 10.0.99.9;
#
        process inject-routes {
                run /home/AFX/qafx.py;
       }
        neighbor 10.0.99.4{
                description ""EXA_AFX2_2_IAVRR"";
                hold-time 90;
                add-path send;
                family {
                        ipv4 mpls-vpn;
                        ipv6 mpls-vpn;
                }
        }

```

##### IMPORTANCE
blocker for utilizing this application in a production environment

",{},{}
