12684,IssuesEvent,2016-02-14 20:19:22+00:00,36759907,graphistry/pygraphistry,4249447,lmeyerov,6157633,graphistry,opened,More graceful iframe loading failure handling,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/graphistry/pygraphistry/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/graphistry/pygraphistry/labels/p2', 'name': 'p2', 'color': 'fbca04'}]",[],0,"( + @thibaudh @padentomasello @briantrice )

