12823,IssuesEvent,2017-03-10 18:44:16+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,218689,havocp,6392739,conda,opened,Version constraint ignored depending on order of args to `conda create` (4.3.13),[],[],0,"All of these command lines should resolve `python=2.7.12` I think but some choose `python=2.7.13`.
