CLI Version: azure-cli (2.0.22)**

OS Type: Win

Installation via: npm / brew / win-or-mac installer / docker / github repo

Mode: ARM

Environment: **AzureCloud

Description:
H:>az vm create --resource-group test --name karunsnapshotvm01-22 --attach-os-disk https://testpre.blob.core.windows.net/testpremium/KarunVMUnmanaged01-2220180122141458.vhd --os-type linux
