13269,IssuesEvent,2016-09-16 21:28:26+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,5723682,tjprescott,6844498,Azure,closed,[Network] Support new 2016-06-01 operations,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Azure/azure-cli/labels/Network', 'name': 'Network', 'color': 'd4c5f9'}]","[{'login': 'tjprescott', 'id': 5723682, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5723682?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/tjprescott', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/tjprescott/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",1,"With API version 2016-06-01, there are new operations that didn't exist before.
Add these operations to the CLI.

From a diff between the following files, I found the new operations listed below:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs/master/arm-network/2016-03-30/swagger/network.json
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs/master/arm-network/2016-06-01/swagger/network.json

- [x] `nic get-effective-route-table`
- [x] `nic list-effective-nsg`
- [x] `vnet peering delete`
- [x] `vnet peering show`
- [x] `vnet peering create`
- [x] `vnet peering update` (generic update)
- [x] `vnet peering list`
- [x] `vnet check-ip-address`
",{},{}
