13508,IssuesEvent,2017-06-26 06:58:41+00:00,13258039,aio-libs/aiohttp,356399,asvetlov,7049303,aio-libs,closed,Add underscore prefix to all modules except web,[],[],8,"I see a lot of aiohttp import mis-usage.

While everywhere in docs we do promote `import aiohttp` for client API and `from aiohttp import web` for server one people constantly do something like `from aiohttp.web.web_response import Response`.

