13928,IssuesEvent,2016-04-12 09:06:24+00:00,1199632,schematics/schematics,7081785,bintoro,7866441,schematics,closed,Schematics vs pylint - can I get there from here?,[],[],7,"I have a pretty bare-bones module taken almost straight from the front page demo in the docs:

