from schematics.types import SHA1Type, StringType, URLType

class Account(Model):
    name = StringType(required=True)
    hashed_password = SHA1Type(required=True)
    website = URLType()
```

It works exactly as expected and I don't have any problems with it, except that pylint 1.2.1 goes nuts on it:

```
