14913,IssuesEvent,2017-03-11 16:43:40+00:00,14284859,marshmallow-code/marshmallow,2379650,sloria,10334301,marshmallow-code,closed,TypeError - unexpected keyword argument 'ordered',"[{'id': 65183466, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/marshmallow/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'fc2929', 'default': True}]",[],6,"When running our tests with marshmallow-2.13.2 and marshmallow-jsonapi-0.10.2, we encountered this stack trace:

