15393,IssuesEvent,2016-06-24 16:23:53+00:00,23924195,Lasagne/Lasagne,629706,f0k,11752110,Lasagne,opened,Add `shared_axes` argument to DropoutLayer,[],[],0,"As discussed in #701, adding a `shared_axes` argument to `DropoutLayer` would allow several additional use cases for dropout:
* shared_axes=(): standard dropout
* shared_axes=(0): batch-wise dropout (use the same dropout mask across axis 0)
* shared_axes=(2,3): drop full feature maps (use the same dropout mask across axes 2 and 3)
* shared_axes=(1,2): drop full frequency bands of spectrograms (use the same dropout mask across axes 1 and 2)

In addition, we could have a `spatial_dropout()` shortcut (possibly coordinate the naming with whatever we decide for #626).",{},{}
