15451,IssuesEvent,2015-06-17 21:36:29+00:00,22783065,project-generator/project_generator,2963726,0xc0170,11992191,project-generator,opened,Replace jinja2 templates by project templates,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/project-generator/project_generator/labels/type:%20feature', 'name': 'type: feature', 'color': '84b6eb'}]",[],0,"Relates to #149, as pgen will get project parsing support (a user provides own project aka template), most of jinja2 templates should be replaced by exporter dictionaries.

Each exporter will have a dictinary which is 1:1 mapping to the project files. This dictionary will be adjusted to the user's input (template, yaml files), then exported.

