16924,IssuesEvent,2017-03-13 16:54:17+00:00,1553944,wireservice/csvkit,151276,eric-brechemier,17111824,wireservice,opened,Alpha2 ISO country for Namibia (NA) is silently discarded,[],[],0,"This is quite unexpected. Probably related to #49.

