/usr/local/include/pybind11/functional.h:26:18:   required from ‘struct pybind11::detail::type_caster<std::function<_Res(_ArgTypes ...)> >::load(pybind11::handle, bool) [with Return = std::shared_ptr<Car>; Args = {int, int}]::<lambda(int, int)>’
/usr/local/include/pybind11/functional.h:26:15:   required from ‘bool pybind11::detail::type_caster<std::function<_Res(_ArgTypes ...)> >::load(pybind11::handle, bool) [with Return = std::shared_ptr<Car>; Args = {int, int}]’
