17148,IssuesEvent,2016-09-14 00:54:30+00:00,26516210,certbot/certbot,6504915,bmw,17889013,certbot,opened,Understand other TLS protocols for Nginx,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/certbot/certbot/labels/nginx', 'name': 'nginx', 'color': 'ff8420'}]",[],0,"When installing a certificate to a user's Nginx config, we make see a server block containing:
