17470,IssuesEvent,2017-02-20 18:57:45+00:00,51625787,vatlab/SOS,9889312,BoPeng,20074389,vatlab,closed,Auxiliary step problem ,"[{'id': 325435536, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/vatlab/SOS/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'fc2929', 'default': True}, {'id': 540146120, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/vatlab/SOS/labels/question', 'name': 'question', 'color': '006b75', 'default': True}]",[],49,"I hope it is just my undoing but I cannot seem to make this example the backward `make` style:

