17482,IssuesEvent,2018-04-24 04:01:22+00:00,51625787,vatlab/SoS,917985,gaow,20074389,vatlab,opened,`dryrun` get caught in infinite loop,[],[],0,"I've noticed this issue for a while but did not find a motivation to fix it until today: I've got asked by someone to provide pure scripts from my workflow, so I did a `dryrun`. But I got caught in an infinite loop. To reproduce, 

```
